{"tid":819068,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"靈恩派係邪教？為什麼靚女都去了靈恩派教會？","createTime":"2018-09-14T13:52:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T04:28:49.000Z","uid":20816,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d77a602fc9f25337d0b3b7793a5a6a3f64a1aeda","tid":819068,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T13:52:53.000Z","msg":"有一件不方便說的真相，就是靚女都去了靈恩派教會。只是，有沒有人想過，這是出於什麼原因？<br />\n<br />\n有一節經文，基要派教會很喜歡用的，就是林前1:26：「弟兄們哪，可見你們蒙召的，按著肉體有智慧的不多，有能力的不多，有尊貴的也不多。」再讀下去，「神卻揀選了世上愚拙的，叫有智慧的羞愧（考不上大學的得安慰了）&hellip;&hellip;又揀選了世上軟弱的，叫那強壯的羞愧（那沒做GYM沒魚尾線常常感冒的得安慰了）&hellip;&hellip;神也揀選了世上卑賤的（做文員仔和七仔的得安慰了）&hellip;&hellip;被人厭惡的（人緣不好和夏天有體臭的得安慰了）&hellip;&hellip;以及那無有的（買六合彩又沒中奬的得安慰了）&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n我想，在靈恩派教會聚會的信徒，從未想到可以如此有創意的用以上經文來得安慰，因為他們聽得最多的，是成功，成功和成功。又哪來老弱殘廢？瞧，連四肢不全的Nick，都比你我賺得多耶！<br />\n<br />\n為什麼返福音派教會的，總是斯文長裙四眼娘？為什麼返靈恩派的，總是吊帶小背心短裙索女？這種分別太明顯了，不可能是偶然的。最簡單的解釋，是福音派教會保守，如果你穿得太少，會送來披肩，告訴你：「冷氣大啊，姊妹，披上它吧！」而靈恩派，很善解人意，從不留難你的髮型和衣著。<br />\n<br />\n我相信，上述解釋並不足夠。<br />\n<br />\n更好的說法是：靚女比眼鏡娘經驗更多成功，這剛好呼應靈恩派的成功神學。她恆常的經歷，是「人見人愛、車見車載」。她在靈恩派教會聽到的是，只要正能量就得成功，只要祈禱祈爆，上帝就把恩典倒下來。這種講法，其實十分切合她的經歷。<br />\n<br />\n除了靚，還有有錢，對一個人怎理解世界和自身經歷也是決定性的。就像王菀之曾不以為然的說：「人家說娛樂圈好黑暗，我進來看過，不是這樣差啊！」因為她有錢，她不用上床換機會，輕輕就跨過這些泥濘，不用像沒錢的女生，要苦思一晚是否跟監製上床換取一個角色。有錢令她如在天空飛行，無視地上踏過泥濘者的掙扎。<br />\n<br />\n有錢、美貌、高學歷，都能輕易帶來成功，他們若成為信徒，靈恩派講正能量、雅比斯的禱告、可能思想，就正符合他們的成功，解釋他們的經歷。<br />\n<br />\n有女生拿下奧運金牌，一夜成名，她回到教會，你估她想聽什麼？當然是為她拿下下一面金牌禱告啊，難道要聽你說：「神揀選了世上軟弱的，叫那強壯的羞愧」？一個靚女來教會，當然想開開心心，受眾人注目（正如她一向就是如此受注目），難道想聽你說：「不要以外面的辮頭髮，戴金飾，穿美衣為妝飾，只要以裡面存著長久溫柔，安靜的心為妝飾；這在神面前是極寶貴的。」（彼前3:3-4）<br />\n筆者不才，面對靚女也是這樣潑冷水。所以，筆者牧養之下，靚女都跑掉了。"},{"pid":"a2e09d5857b07cbaadc13642912fe48851120f1d","tid":819068,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T13:53:41.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"ee04062effa5199a0d57cf9983acc7e673f8bccf","tid":819068,"uid":99816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T13:54:49.000Z","msg":"正解<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05101631c809f48ac300fc1a1c1dfceef2989772","tid":819068,"uid":99816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2e09d5857b07cbaadc13642912fe48851120f1d","tid":819068,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T13:53:41.000Z","msg":"10"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T13:55:00.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"32e00acf9c7f47f64c048dd53c02fe811091b46b","tid":819068,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T13:56:19.000Z","msg":"傳銷"},{"pid":"2464fad4522ae8bb66e5f120df6fb595bd1d17f8","tid":819068,"uid":20816,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T13:56:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.church611.org/images/20151224_Awakening/main/14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.church611.org%2Fimages%2F20151224_Awakening%2Fmain%2F14.jpg&h=111206c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個算唔算？"},{"pid":"c52dfb85bc05ac3a2da4f3bb7adda0e1434129b3","tid":819068,"uid":23400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05101631c809f48ac300fc1a1c1dfceef2989772","tid":819068,"uid":99816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2e09d5857b07cbaadc13642912fe48851120f1d","tid":819068,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T13:53:41.000Z","msg":"10"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T13:55:00.000Z","msg":"9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T13:56:57.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"f5ffe015f54028d50fcb04ebb3337324d084d7d8","tid":819068,"uid":28800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T13:58:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bfd6d8cb068c7d582691a789b438326233225f44","tid":819068,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T13:59:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1676270/org/66f9c506191bb101c615e1ea8f072f99.png/Wm3JDRdLwwvnU1A3e1yoYC2AQ23AAkLfgxkyQoMZMkI?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1676270%2Forg%2F66f9c506191bb101c615e1ea8f072f99.png%2FWm3JDRdLwwvnU1A3e1yoYC2AQ23AAkLfgxkyQoMZMkI%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=dc3d3ef1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>警方再搗破兩間倫敦金詐騙集團拘54人，年齡介乎16至38歲，包括董事、股東、負責人及經紀。警方扣押多輛涉案波子、寶馬名車，香港01記者翻查兩車車主身份，發現有人年紀輕輕，曾任職多間有經營「倫敦金」的金融公司，更曾用「副總裁」職銜，以「無上限佣金」作招徠，在fb招攬應屆DSE考生入行。他們更用大額支票及名車照片炫富，以證明其高收入及高消費，騙取客戶信心。有網頁起底，公開他們的資料及疑涉行騙的罪行。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n起底網列車主事跡　疑長期做倫敦金詐騙<br />\n<br />\n警方在行動中扣押三輛名車，包括兩輛保時捷及一輛寶馬跑車。根據運輸署資料，黑色保時捷的車主為一名姓歐陽的男子，登記地址為牛頭角康麗園，車輛登記日期為2010年，車價市值約123萬元。有起底網頁指，一名與車主同名的男子已婚，曾在多間有投資倫敦金的金融公司工作，疑長期進行倫敦金詐騙。他報稱經常高額消費，以製造倫敦金獲利豐厚的假象，令更多人入局。<br />\n<br />\n吸引年輕人賺快錢　包括應屆Dse考生<br />\n<br />\n網頁又指，歐陽多次以「豐厚工資」、「前途好」等言詞招聘人手，吸引年輕人賺快錢而投身成為騙徒。根據歐陽的個人facebook戶口，可見他以「副總裁」的身份發文招攬新人，包括應屆Dse考生，他稱﹕<span style=\"color: red;\">「男人最緊要有上進心，唔好怕失敗，有心搵錢我唔會畀你失敗」</span>，並指願意花兩個月時間親自教授新人，薪酬是底薪及無上限佣金 。他亦曾展示大額支票，吸引年輕人入行。<br />\n<br />\n至於白色寶馬跑車，根據運輸署資料，車主為一名姓董男子，登記地址為大圍美田邨，車輛登記日期為2013年，該車當時市值約44萬元。根據網上資料，一名與車主同名的姓董男子現年24歲，疑一直從事涉及倫敦金騙案，他過往曾在其他金融公司工作，與歐陽曾經是同事，兩人關係密切。他被指有黑社會背景，曾被判縱火案罪成，判入懲教所。有網頁指他多次誘騙他人參與倫敦金，又貼出現金照，吹噓倫敦金回報，導致多人損失慘重，他亦公然在社交網站招攬人手。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/214237/%E5%80%AB%E6%95%A6%E9%87%91%E9%A8%99%E6%A1%88-%E6%B3%A2%E5%AD%90%E5%AF%B6%E9%A6%AC%E7%82%AB%E5%AF%8C-%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8Dmk%E7%94%B7%E8%B5%B7%E5%BA%95-fb%E6%8B%9Bdse%E8%80%83%E7%94%9F%E5%85%A5%E8%A1%8C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F214237%2F%25E5%2580%25AB%25E6%2595%25A6%25E9%2587%2591%25E9%25A8%2599%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25AF%25B6%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E7%2582%25AB%25E5%25AF%258C-%25E9%2587%2591%25E8%259E%258Dmk%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E5%25BA%2595-fb%25E6%258B%259Bdse%25E8%2580%2583%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%2585%25A5%25E8%25A1%258C&d=jtxzMWEAjToVXpklrv0%2FE1eK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=b9c9b63b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/214237/%E5%80%AB%E6%95%A6%E9%87%91%E9%A8%99%E6%A1%88-%E6%B3%A2%E5%AD%90%E5%AF%B6%E9%A6%AC%E7%82%AB%E5%AF%8C-%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8Dmk%E7%94%B7%E8%B5%B7%E5%BA%95-fb%E6%8B%9Bdse%E8%80%83%E7%94%9F%E5%85%A5%E8%A1%8C</a>"},{"pid":"11288c6f71c135fbd25ee6f425ee75e5babd0364","tid":819068,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:00:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.church611.org/slider/youth/PSScamp/20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.church611.org%2Fslider%2Fyouth%2FPSScamp%2F20.jpg&h=156b36d4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e2a680ecf498c0700b60c5b681ecd7da3c07c787","tid":819068,"uid":165213,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:02:16.000Z","msg":"蠢人 無獨立思考先會信<br />\n呢d女屌完就算 做老婆咪搞"},{"pid":"d5f9304765cf264ce717b66c9bfff78c95ae6583","tid":819068,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:05:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"14b28b9c3d950a8839bbd0e15e5932e74c9ab51d","tid":819068,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5f9304765cf264ce717b66c9bfff78c95ae6583","tid":819068,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:05:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:06:46.000Z","msg":"Why?"},{"pid":"7d1c5d2d2d6a4fca54e8bd09d07cdaee2c8be250","tid":819068,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T04:28:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9761841b5bd6af657b74551d5fe33e595251468d","tid":819068,"uid":67338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T04:28:49.000Z","msg":"有幾靚呀?<br />\n<br />\n睇過"}]}